description: Erection of a part 13, part, 18 and part 25 storey building comprising residential development with associated residential parking and amenity space, landscape works and all necessary ancillary and enabling works.  (summary)
decision_conditions:
The development hereby permitted shall be begun no later than the  expiration of three years from the date of this permission.

Reason: In order to comply with the requirements of Section 91 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.
